I"%
<ol>
  <li>点击你想开始编号的页面的最开始</li>
  <li>选择<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Layout (or Page Layout) &gt; Breaks &gt; Next Page.</code></li>
</ol>

<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20181226094653663.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tld2VpMTY4,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="" /></p>

<ol>
  <li>在起始页（插入section break的那页），进入页眉页脚的Design选项，取消Link to Previous</li>
</ol>

<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2018122609531356.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述" /></p>

<ol>
  <li>Insert &gt; Page Number插入页码，并选择从1（任意你想要的数字）开始编号</li>
</ol>

<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20181226095025324.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tld2VpMTY4,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述" /></p>

<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20181226095329234.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tld2VpMTY4,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述" /></p>

<ol>
  <li>大功告成</li>
</ol>

<p>Tips:
有时候文章的页眉会出现一条横线，如下图</p>

<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20190312155715973.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述" /></p>

<p>想去掉这个横线的话，很容易，只需要双击页眉进入编辑模式，然后点击格式刷即可</p>

<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20190312155850130.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tld2VpMTY4,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述" /></p>

